Detect if support: 
```javascript
try {
	var isFileSaverSupported = !!new Blob;
	alert(isFileSaverSupported); // true
} catch (e) {}
```

Example (tested and supported in Chrome 44.0.2403.157, Windows 8.1 & Chrome for Android 44.0.2403.133, Android 5.0.1, but not supported in Dolphin 11.4.17 or Dolphin 11.4.17 with Jetpack engine):
```javascript
try {
	alert('Start'); // shows in Dolphin
	saveAs(new Blob(), 'test');  // doesn't call in Dolphin
	alert('Finish'); // shows in Dolphin
} catch (e) {
	alert('Something wrong'); // doesn't show in Dolphin
}
```

and this works fine (so it can save a file):
```html
<a href="example.zip">Download</a>
```

